  "keyFeatures": [
    "Universal file conversion across all media types (images, videos, audio, documents, code, archives, etc.)",
    "100% browser-based with client-side processing for privacy",
    "60+ format handlers using WebAssembly (FFmpeg, ImageMagick, Pandoc, SQLite, etc.)",
    "Intelligent conversion path finding between formats",
